    {
      "id": "blank-tutorial-instructions",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Start here",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 290,
        "y": 725
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bootstrap Tutorial\n\nThis walkthrough proves the **graph-native handshake** end to end.\n\nYou will:\n1. Copy the onboarding prompt from the bootstrap node\n2. Paste it into your AI chat\n3. Copy the returned **JSON transaction**\n4. Paste it back into Twilite and watch the node advance\n\nOnce the handshake works, you are ready to start a fresh graph."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "blank-tutorial-step-copy",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 1",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 290,
        "y": 1010
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 210,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 1 — Copy the prompt\n\nClick **Copy onboarding prompt** in the **Bootstrap Handshake** node.\n\nPaste that prompt into your AI chat exactly as-is so the model answers in Twilite's transaction format."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "blank-tutorial-step-paste",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 2",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 290,
        "y": 1245
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 2 — Paste the transaction\n\nYour AI should answer with **JSON only**: a small `transaction`, not a full graph.\n\nCopy that response and paste it into the **Bootstrap Handshake** node.\n\nIf needed, you can also use the toolbar **Paste** action and drop the transaction onto the canvas."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "blank-tutorial-finish",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Finish",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 290,
        "y": 1510
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 3 — Open a fresh graph\n\nWhen the bootstrap node confirms the import:\n\n1. Click **New File** in the toolbar\n2. Use **Dismiss** on the welcome screen to land on a clean canvas\n3. Start building with a chat that already knows the handshake\n\nOptional: add reference images or documents before you begin."
      }
    },
